Company Overview of Geller Family Office Services LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Geller Family Office Services LLC offers finance, accounting, tax, and family office services to wealthy individuals and families. Its financial services include financial planning, investment planning and oversight, cash management and financial reporting, and tax planning and compliance. The company is based in New York, New York. Geller Family Office Services LLC operates as a subsidiary of Geller & Company LLC.


909 Third AvenueNew York, NY 10022United States



Phone: 212-583-6001

www.gellerfamilyofficeservices.com







