Welcome to 
Geller & Company





Family Office Services
We take the time to understand the intricacies of your financial life.



Learn More





Corporate Financial & Advisory Services
Keen financial insights for superior decision making.


Learn More





Non-Profit & Foundation Financial Services
Leverage your wealth to change the world.


Learn More



 



Geller & Company serves two distinct types of clients; individuals and families who are private wealth owners, and business owners and senior management who are responsible for the financial affairs of a company.
For wealth owners, we provide integrated wealth management services that help turn your financial success into enduring personal wealth. We focus on a wide range of needs that wealth owners have in the areas of investments, tax, philanthropy, estate planning and cash management. 
For business owners and senior management, we are an outsourced partner for all financial strategies, planning, accounting and reporting functions of the organization. We help increase shareholder value and manage the complexity of running the financial operations that support large companies.



We Are Advocates for Our Clients
             Our strong advocacy on behalf of clients begins with a thorough understanding of your goals and what it takes to get you there. We take a comprehensive approach to managing financial matters and have experts in all the disciplines required to help you succeed.



We Are Independent & Objective
We are a privately held, fee based firm working solely on behalf of our clients. We never take payments from third party service providers that could create a conflict of interest with our clients.  

We Are Adept at Managing ComplexityIntellectual curiosity runs deep in our organization and attracts us to the complexities of managing large scale and intricate financial challenges. Our people are among the best in the industry. Problem solving has helped foster a collaborative organization with our clients, and with the network of professionals with whom we work daily. We've seen complexity first-hand and our people are experienced in managing it effectively and efficiently.  
                 
  
We Are Grounded in Security & TechnologyWe ensure the highest levels of confidentiality, privacy, security, disaster recovery and regulatory compliance for very large corporate clients, and we're able to model these same standards of service for every client we serve. We continue to make significant and ongoing investments in technology to allow our clients to leverage their inherent strengths without compromising privacy and security. 
                  
		      









About Geller & Company
Founded in 1984, Geller & Company is a premier, strategic, financial advisory firm whose clients include wealth owners and their families as well as senior management and owners who work in a corporate environment. 
