How do I update this listing?




                                             Geller Family Office Services is based out of New York. Geller Family Office Services is a large advisory firm with  26-100 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $2,469,297,781 (Form ADV from 2016-09-01).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $184,965,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 97.74%. Geller Family Office Services's largest holding is SPDR S&P 500 ETF Index Depositary Receipts with shares held of 329,571.  Geller Family Office Services has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 48 13F filings in our database for Geller Family Office Services. 
                                           






